<section class="service-main">
  <div class="service-main-grid">

    <div class="service-content">

      <!-- Overview -->
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="content-label">Overview</div>
        <h2 class="content-h2">Why <em>Native Joint Preservation</em> Matters</h2>
        <p class="content-p">
          Your natural knee, hip, and spine are irreplaceable. No prosthetic implant — however advanced — fully replicates the feel, range of motion, and longevity of your own joint. <strong>Dr. Sarish Sharma's philosophy is simple:</strong> protect what you have for as long as possible using the most effective non-surgical treatments available.
        </p>
        <p class="content-p">
          Joint degeneration is a spectrum. Caught early to mid-stage, the progression can be significantly slowed — and in many cases, pain eliminated — without ever reaching the point of needing replacement. Even in advanced cases, targeted interventions can provide years of meaningful pain relief and function.
        </p>

        <div class="preserve-stats">
          <div class="preserve-stat">
            <div class="preserve-stat-num">8,000+</div>
            <div class="preserve-stat-label">Patients treated<br>without surgery</div>
          </div>
          <div class="preserve-stat">
            <div class="preserve-stat-num">15+</div>
            <div class="preserve-stat-label">Years specialising<br>in joint preservation</div>
          </div>
          <div class="preserve-stat">
            <div class="preserve-stat-num">92%</div>
            <div class="preserve-stat-label">Avoid surgery<br>success rate</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Conditions — Tabbed -->
      <div class="content-section">
        <div class="content-label">Conditions Treated</div>
        <h2 class="content-h2">What We <em>Treat</em></h2>
        <p class="content-p">Select a joint area below to see the conditions treated under that category.</p>

        <div class="condition-tabs">
          <div class="tab-btns">
            <button class="tab-btn active" onclick="switchTab('knee', this)">Knee</button>
            <button class="tab-btn" onclick="switchTab('hip', this)">Hip</button>
